casebody.data:
Michael DARBY, Appellant-Movant,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Respondent. M-1130/1131 Sept. Term 2018
082875 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 21, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal (M-1130) is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the miscellaneous motion to "dispose of the motion for leave to appeal solely on the basis of the moving papers" (M-1131) is denied.
